Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,兔子罗杰是小说与电影的一个卡通人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,该电影中的洗脑欢乐主题曲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,赞颂黑人克服种种困难  以及对美国历史的贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,哈勃定律通常被用来推算遥远星系的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,玻璃天花板是指女性和少数族裔无法晋升到决策层的无形障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,兔子罗杰的电影名为《谁陷害了兔子罗杰》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:06.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,德国纳粹旗  该卐与佛教的卍相反
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:04.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:06.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我是谢尔顿·库珀博士\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm Dr. Sheldon Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:10.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎收看由谢尔顿·库珀出品的《有趣的旗帜》\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And welcome to Sheldon Cooper Presents: Fun with Flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,最终集  壮丽的旗帜\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the Final Episode Flagtacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道会有拉炮  还是吓死人家了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I knew it was coming. Still scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们一定在想"居然最终集了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now, I'm sure you're thinking, "The final episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁要害你们变成旗帜盲了"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}who will stand between us and flag ignorance"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,像我就有这个想法\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I know I was thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.62,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这是旗帜节目还是读心节目啊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Is this a show on flags or mind reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:34.38,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但事实上是因为我无法继续兼顾全职工作\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}But the truth is I can no longer balance a full-time career,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:37.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,热门网络节目  以及女朋友了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}a popular Internet show, and a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他是真的有女朋友  你们这些留言的混球们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And he really does have one, you jerks on the comment board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:45.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,常言道  天下无不散之筵席\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So as they say, all good things must come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:48.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然仅有232集视觉飨宴\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}After only 232 episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,如果某人有次\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}233 if we include the one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.93,0:00:54.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,没忘了按下录制键  那应该是233集\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}somebody forgot to press record on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,说好了不提那事儿\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You said you weren't gonna bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:58.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,说好了你会按录制键\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And you said you pressed record.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,总之  用放松的姿势\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Anyway, please sit back, relax,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我们一起跑完这最后一圈\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and join us as we take our final lap...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就像这只赛车旗指示的一样\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}...as indicated by the waving of this racing flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:12.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,白旗在不同系列车赛中有不同意义\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}有些代表场上有慢速车辆  有些则是最后一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,当然  白旗也代表"举白旗投降"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}And, of course, white flags can also represent surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,刚铎宰相  日本源氏也都使用白旗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}the Stewards of Gondor, and the Japanese Minamoto clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:18.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,刚铎宰相  《魔戒》中刚铎地区的统治者\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}日本源氏与平家大战时  一家白旗  一家红旗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:18.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但想必你们肯定还记得这些\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}but I'm sure you remember that from episode 62,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:21.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,因为62集"白旗  谁举白旗及缘由"都讲过\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}"White Flags: Who's Wavin' 'Em and Why""
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那集超赞\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That was a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是赞到爆炸\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:58.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来以为清理过世教授的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know, I thought cleaning out a dead professor's office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,办公室会很无聊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}was gonna just be boring,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不过在我发现他的假牙后\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}but then I found his dentures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:05.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我才意识到是无聊加恶心\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and realized it's also gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,艾伯特教授的家人不想要这些东西吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Doesn't Professor Abbott's family want any of this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得他好像没家人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't think he had a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,-真惨  -是啊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- That's rough. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:14.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,一生都奉献给了工作\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You can spend your whole life working,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:18.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,最后留下的只有盒子里的一些研究资料\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and at the end all that's left are some papers in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不禁让你思索人生\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Makes you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.37,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:26.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都得仔细检查过这些东西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey. Hey, we're supposed to look through all this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,以确保不会扔掉什么重要资料\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}before we throw it away in case it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,看啦  不是太旧就是被拒[反证]的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I-I did. It's all outdated or disproved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不一定哦  这支旧笔"证明"了重力存在\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know. This old pen kind of proves gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:37.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,翻转过来  小人偶的泳衣就掉下来\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}When I tilt it, her bathing suit falls right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸以前也有一支这样的笔\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, my dad used to have a pen like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:43.29,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我整个六年级都跟它"约"会\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I dated it all through sixth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:44.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,还是感觉很奇怪\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}It still feels weird
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样把这些研究成果都扔掉\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}just throwing away his work like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不用难过\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,未来某天  也会有人来扔你的研究报告\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Someday, someone will be throwing out your work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:55.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是谢尔顿  而那个某天是昨天\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That someone was Sheldon, and the day was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你们瞧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,"亲爱的罗杰  在你获得首次重大发现时开\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}"Dear Roger, to be opened upon your first great discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,爱你  妈"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Love, Mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧这日期\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Wow, look at the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:09.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他留了整整50年  却从没有机会开\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}He saved this 50 years and never got to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人惋惜\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的罗杰·艾伯特\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Poor Roger Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,罗杰特听起来像罗杰兔\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Roger Abbott sounds just like Roger Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,罗杰特  罗杰特  罗杰兔\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Roger Abbott, Roger Abbott, Roger Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.22,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  莱纳德  我知道这对死者不敬\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, my God, Leonard, I know he's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你念念看  超好笑啊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}but try it. It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,罗杰特  罗杰特  罗杰兔\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Roger Abbott, Roger Rabbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,佩妮\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Penny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我的年度最佳新人\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, my rookie of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,丹  我一开始不想雇我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, Dan. My boss who didn't want to hire me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在超爱抱我的老板\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and now's a little hug machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:44.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你  新加入不久就业绩第三名\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, look at you. Brand-new and already the third best sales rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,-过来我那桌坐坐吧  -我马上过去\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- Why don't you come over to my table. - Yes. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,伯纳黛特还在停车\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Bernadette's just parking the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.74,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,伯纳黛特  人萌音甜\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Bernadette. Cute, sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,恶毒凶残的小伯纳黛特\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}vicious little Bernadette.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样嘛  她没那么坏\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Come on. She's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,公司野餐的时候  她吼了我跟我孙子\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}At the company picnic she yelled at me and my grandson
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们输了二人三腿赛跑\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}for losing the three-legged race.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:08.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我孙子现在还叫她为"毒舌大奶娃"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I mean, he still calls her "That mean kid with the big boobies."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她有时候是有点凶  但我保证\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I know she can be a little intense, but, I swear,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,等稍微熟了之后   她就是很亲切的一个人了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}she is so sweet once you get past all the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在聊什么\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在聊有多喜欢跟你共事\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We were just talking about how much we love working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:18.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,丹\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,在《有趣的旗帜》的这些岁月里\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Over the years here at Fun With Flags,
