Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想从您这打听艾伯特教授的信息\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We're trying to get some information about Professor Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在清理他的办公室时\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}We were cleaning out his office
