Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,您知道这是什么吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Any chance you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,知道  他总是在搞这玩意\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, he was always working on this.
