Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是某个遥远星系的摄动角度\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}That could be the angle of perturbation of a distant galaxy.
