Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真相不是那么有趣\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sorry it's not more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,往好的方面想  你们不必听\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}On the bright side, you didn't have to listen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,他35年来肚子饿得咕噜叫的声音\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}to his stomach growl for 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那艾伯特教授这辈子研究的东西\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, was there anything that Professor Abbott worked on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,难道没有半点算得上是成就的东西吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}during his life that came close to an accomplishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:21.79,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说  他的研究一无所成\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}To be honest, his research never amounted to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你是他的同事\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh. You were his colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你的研究结果如何\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}How did your research turn out?
