Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:28.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,得诺贝尔奖的人  都住这种"豪宅"\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey, this is the apartment you get when you win a Nobel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以是一个很简朴的人啊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Well, you could be very frugal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是受够了每个人都在说反话了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm getting a little tired of everybody's sarcasm.
