Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我是表现得有那么一点强势\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I mean, maybe I come off a little strong,
