Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然可以啊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}No. That's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,但强硬跟告诉你的朋友\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}but there's a difference between being tough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她的新裤子像一块松垮的尿布\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}and telling your friend her new pants
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.98,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,这两者还是有区别的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}look like a saggy diaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我的确那么说了  是吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I did say that, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你说了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时超级难为情  我只好把裤子退了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I felt so self-conscious, I had to return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,退到哪儿  婴儿用品店吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Where? To Babies R Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.16,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're doing it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.79,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我们可以走了吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}Okay, sorry. Can we just go?
