Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,-我还是走吧  -不  坐下\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}- I think I'd rather go. - No, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,你哪儿也不许去  知道吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}You are not going anywhere, all right?
