Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,我想花一点时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'd like to take a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,亲自谢谢艾米·费拉·福勒博士\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}to personally thank Dr. Amy Farrah Fowler,
