Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,她是第一位搭档主持关于旗帜\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs16\1c&H3CA8DC&}is the first woman to co-host a flag
